    <bioghist>
      <head>Historical Information
</head>
      <p>Montgomery County, named for Richard Montgomery, was formed from Fincastle County in 1776. Part of Botetourt County was added in 1790 and part of Pulaski County was added in 1842.
</p>
    </bioghist>
